Foschini Says Full-Year Earnings Per Share Expected to Rise as Much as 22%

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-04-18T13:32:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-18/foschini-says-full-year-earnings-per-share-expected-to-rise-as-much-as-22-.html
Foschini Group Ltd. (TFG)  said basic
earnings per share for the 12 months through March are expected
to be between 19 percent and 22 percent higher than a year
earlier.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  